Class AngleSliderUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.plaf.ComponentUI
      • javax.swing.plaf.SliderUI
        • com.pump.plaf.AngleSliderUI
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AquaAngleSliderUI

    public class AngleSliderUI
extends javax.swing.plaf.SliderUI
    This UI renders a JSlider as a circular dial, and then value of the slider represents an angle from [0,2*pi).

    This class (and subclasses) can not respond to several slider properties such as orientation, inversion, tickmarks, labels, etc.
